{"type":null,"faqId":32890,"title":"使用流光快门的车水马龙模式怎样能拍出较好的效果","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body45863669\"><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033750060__p51706359\">建议在高楼或天桥上拍摄夜晚车流快速移动的场景，且拍摄时间不易过长。不建议在距离较近时拍摄，一方面车灯的轨迹较短，难以获得较长而连续的轨迹；另一方面近距离时车大灯的强度会使照片过曝。</p></div><div></div></body>","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0033750060","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748441000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10,PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-TL11H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":12,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"车水马龙,使用,相机,流光快门,光绘涂鸦","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}